languages.text: "Моя исповедь окончена. Я обнажил перед тобой свое нутро и скрытую в нем правду — ты вол{mf|ен|ьна} поступать с ней как знаешь".

languages.text: 「告白は終わりだ。私は自分の内面をすべてさらけ出し、隠された真実までも伝えた。その真実をどうするかは、お前次第だ」
languages.original_text: "My confession is over. I have bared my innermost self before you, and the truth concealed therein. You are free to do with it as you please."

traits.locale_text: 「告白は終わりだ。私は自分の内面をすべてさらけ出し、隠された真実までも伝えた。その真実をどうするかは、お前次第だ」

languages.text: «Mi confesión ha terminado. He desnudado a mi yo más íntimo y la verdad que oculta ante usted. Es libre de hacer con ello lo que le plazca».
languages.original_text: "My confession is over. I have bared my innermost self before you, and the truth concealed therein. You are free to do with it as you please."

languages.text: "Meine Beichte ist beendet. Ich habe Euch mein Innerstes offenbart und die darin verborgene Wahrheit. Ihr dürft damit tun, was Ihr möchtet."
languages.original_text: "My confession is over. I have bared my innermost self before you, and the truth concealed therein. You are free to do with it as you please."

languages.text: « Ma confession est terminée. Je me suis entièrement dévoilé à vous et vous connaissez désormais toute la vérité. Libre à vous d'en faire ce que vous voulez. »
languages.original_text: "My confession is over. I have bared my innermost self before you, and the truth concealed therein. You are free to do with it as you please."

languages.text: "İtiraflarım bu kadar. En derinlerimdeki hislerimi ve orada gizlenen gerçeği seninle paylaştım. Bununla ne istersen yapmakta özgürsün."
